OL,3,CProbe designed to study how clouds
OL,4,Caffect Earth's climate launched into
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FA satellite that will look inside
OL,8,Fclouds to help make more accurate
OL,9,Fweather forecasts and climate
OL,10,Fpredictions has been launched into
OL,11,Fspace.
OL,13,FEarthCARE blasted off on SpaceX's
OL,14,FFalcon 9 rocket from Vandenberg Space
OL,15,FForce Base in California.
OL,17,FThe probe will help scientists
OL,18,Funderstand how clouds and aerosols
OL,19,Fsuch as dust and smoke play a role in
OL,20,Fheating and cooling the Earth's
OL,21,Fatmosphere.
