OL,4,Caffect Earth's climate launched into
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FThe satellite will also measure
OL,8,Fradiation emitted by the planet.
OL,10,FMany of its components, including the
OL,11,Fmain structure and two key
OL,12,Finstruments, were built in the UK.
OL,14,FData from EarthCARE ` which stands for
OL,15,FEarth Cloud Aerosol and Radiation
OL,16,FExplorer ` could help in mitigating
OL,17,Fthe threats posed by global warming,
OL,18,Fexperts say.
