OL,3,CProbe designed to study how clouds
OL,4,Caffect Earth's climate launched into
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FBut little is known about how these
OL,8,Fdrive the Earth's climate system.
OL,10,FThe three-year mission, which cost
OL,11,Fmore than 800 million euros (#680
OL,12,Fmillion), is expected to provide
OL,13,Fanswers.
OL,15,FThe UK Space Agency (UKSA) contributed
OL,16,Faround 120 million euros (#102
OL,17,Fmillion) towards the mission over a
OL,18,Fperiod of 20 years.
