OL,4,Caffect Earth's climate launched into
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FThe satellite weighs just over two
OL,8,Ftonnes (2,200kg) and measures a little
OL,9,Fover 17 metres (56ft) in length.
OL,11,FOn board are four instruments that
OL,12,Fwill analyse cloud structures in
OL,13,Fdetail, take images, and measure how
OL,14,Fmuch heat from the Sun is being
OL,15,Ftrapped by clouds.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
