OL,7,FSurrey Satellite Technology (SSTL)
OL,8,Fdeveloped the satellite's MSI (multi-
OL,9,Fspectral imager) instrument, which
OL,10,Fcomes with two cameras, while space
OL,11,Fmanufacturer Thales Alenia Space UK
OL,12,Fsupplied the broadband radiometer
OL,13,Finstrument, which will provide
OL,14,Fmeasurements of the reflected solar
OL,15,Fand emitted heat radiation.
OL,17,FAirbus Defence and Space UK was
OL,18,Fresponsible for building EarthCARE's
OL,19,Fbase platform.
